    <div class="main review-item" id="5020404">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5020404/" class="title-link">永恒的经典</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5020404"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2292132/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2292132-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2292132/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Jane</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-07-12"
      class="main-meta">2011-07-12 00:42:17</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5020404_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                          每多看一本鲁迅的书，就会对他多一重认识、多一份敬佩。原来大文豪鲁迅还有学者的一面，且造诣是这么高。学问是相通的，正因为曾经对古代小说下过这样一番考证功夫，为后来写作白话小说奠定了深厚的基础。     全书以浅易的文言写成，不会对看惯白话的我们造成阅读障碍...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 2没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            岳麓书社2010版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5020404_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5020404_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
