        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33554105/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33554105/" class="">第6页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48335885/" class=" " title="Fr.dmg">Fr.dmg</a>
                (只当漂流在异乡)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="33554105">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">
故神话不特为宗教之萌芽，美术所由起，且实为文章之渊源。
</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-11-29 10:32</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>
故神话不特为宗教之萌芽，美术所由起，且实为文章之渊源。
</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
